    dc:description "FIGURES 20–24. Uroseius sorrentinus (Lombardini), deutonymph, right legs I–IV, excluding pretarsus. 20. Leg I, dorsal view; 21. Leg II, dorsal view; 22. Leg III, dorsal view; 23. Leg IV, dorsal view; 24. Detail of dorsal setae." ;
